    "summary": "Turso exposes a REST Platform API, a per-database SQL-over-HTTP API, a hosted MCP server, and the `turso` CLI; all require authentication via Turso-issued tokens or OAuth login.",
    "description": "Turso provides SQLite-compatible databases that can run locally, in the cloud, or in a synced local-first model. Its cloud platform lets users manage organizations, groups, and databases and access those databases remotely.",
